May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'FRIENDSXFACTS Matt LeBlanc admitted in the exit interview for the book 'Friends.. Til' the End" that he had a crush on Jennifer Aniston. Hẹ said, "Now had a little crush on Jen in the very beginning but I think the whole world did too. so what are you going to do?"'.
